<br />
But Why skimp on the details when you can get it all..<br />
<br />
I found the <a href="http://www.buy.com/retail/product.asp?sku=10343936&loc=220" target="_blank">GeForce FX 5200</a> with 128MB of Ram on Buy.com for $78.14. and <b>free shipping</b>. So if you have been looking to upgrade your video card, click on the name above, and check it out. It's the base model for GeForce's new FX line and and nearly over $50.00 of normal retail.<br />
<br />
/bow<br />
<br />
<b>- Kudane</b></font></td></tr></table>
